---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceExplore from '../../components/ServiceExplore.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Cosmetic Dentistry — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Teeth whitening, veneers, and dental bonding in Huntington Beach. Dr. Jason Fu creates natural-looking cosmetic results tailored to your goals. Call (714) 893-2106."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/services">Services</a><span class="sep">/</span><span style="color:#cfe6e2">Cosmetic Dentistry</span></div>
    <span class="tag">Cosmetic dentistry</span>
    <h1>Cosmetic Dentistry</h1>
    <p>A more confident, radiant smile—tailored to you.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a consultation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div>

        <div class="img-ph reveal">
          <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
          <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
          <span class="img-ph-desc">Close-up of bright, natural-looking smile — or before/after style image</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <span class="tag">Overview</span>
          <h2>Results that look and feel like you.</h2>
          <p>Our cosmetic solutions—whitening, veneers, and dental bonding—are designed to enhance your natural beauty. Every treatment is tailored to your goals and designed to look and feel like you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <h3>What We Offer</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Teeth Whitening</li>
            <li>Porcelain Veneers</li>
            <li>Dental Bonding</li>
            <li>Smile Makeover consultations</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Smile close-up, bright and natural — not overly artificial</span>
          </div>

          <h3>The Oasis Approach</h3>
          <p>We start with a conversation—not a sales pitch. Dr. Fu reviews your goals, explains realistic outcomes, and recommends only what's right for your teeth. Results should look like a better version of you, not a different person.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Consultation setting — Dr. Fu reviewing options with patient</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Who Is It For?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Patients with stained, chipped, or uneven teeth</li>
            <li>Anyone looking to refresh their smile before a big event</li>
            <li>People who want subtle, natural-looking improvements</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <span class="tag">Common questions</span>
          <h2 class="prose" style="margin-top:8px">Good to know.</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <details open><summary>How do I know which cosmetic treatment is right for me?</summary><p>Dr. Fu will assess your teeth and discuss your goals during a consultation—we'll recommend only what makes sense for your specific case.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Will cosmetic work look natural?</summary><p>Yes. Our goal is always results that enhance your smile without looking artificial or overdone.</p></details>
            <details><summary>How long do cosmetic results last?</summary><p>It varies by treatment—whitening results can last 1–2 years with maintenance, while veneers and bonding can last many years with proper care.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Can cosmetic work be done if I have cavities or gum issues?</summary><p>We address any underlying health concerns first. Cosmetic work on a healthy foundation lasts longer and looks better.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="scard reveal">
          <div class="hd"><div class="grid-ov"></div><h3>Schedule a smile consultation</h3><p>Consultations typically 30–45 min</p></div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>Flexible appointment slots available</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Most insurance accepted &amp; verified</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg><span>ADA, CDC &amp; OSHA safety protocols</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Schedule a Smile Consultation</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<ServiceExplore />

</Layout>
